Package org.gbif.occurrencestore.download.file

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CitationsFileWriter
    Utility class that creates the citations file using a faceted Solr response.
    DownloadTableBuilder
    Class that wraps the process of creating the occurrence and citation files.
    FileJob
    Holds the job information used by each file writer job/thread.
    OccurrenceFileWriter
    Class that creates a single CSV file using a OccurrenceSearchRequest.
    OccurrenceFileWriter.Configuration
    Utility class that holds the general settings of the OccurrenceFileWriter class.
    OccurrenceMapReader
    Reads a occurrence record from HBase and return it in a Map.
    Result
    Communicates the result of a file creation job.
